  "id": "RAW_18c041e9",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-9）：蚂蚁开源 1 万亿参数 Ling 2.0 系列旗舰模型，基于进化链式思维推动高效推理与长上下文能力新突破",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247499681&idx=1&sn=29a297905be4e82a2d672a02afe7dacd",
  "date": "2025-10-09 10:12:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Ling-1T</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"706\" data-imgfileid=\"100016025\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.612037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41b4c7d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOI1u8mR7DwozibB8rxVr8H3rDtfry1Wlv0xBgkRkzJQSxsSiclnq0VWevQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Ling-1T是Ling 2.0系列中的首个旗舰非思维模型，拥有1万亿总参数，该模型基于Ling 2.0架构，旨在推动高效推理和可扩展认知的极限。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Ling-1T在超过20万亿高质量、推理密集的tokens上进行了预训练，支持最长128K的上下文长度，并在中期和后期训练中采用进化链式思维（Evo-CoT）过程。这一课程大大提高了模型的效率和推理深度，使Ling-1T在多个复杂推理基准上实现了最先进的性能，平衡了准确性和效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ling-1t-3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ling-1t-3</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：HunyuanVision</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"404\" data-imgfileid=\"100016029\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.3509259259259259\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bb00794a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOIteSPw9tfG9UAaYsEwvMDuJDBr7hRWFpia8fX5Edib0mEEgB1LHND7sEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Hunyuan-Vision-1.5 是一款采用 mamba-transformer 混合架构的视觉语言模型，具备先进的多语言多模态理解和推理能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在图像和视频理解、视觉推理以及 3D 空间理解等任务中表现出色，并提供无缝的多语言用户体验，确保在真实世界应用中的流畅表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanvision-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuanvision-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Being-VL-0.5</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"218\" data-imgfileid=\"100016028\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1148\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.18981481481481483\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4a895aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOIT30GRbTQB0z8pb52QoQF4iaOcnrNqT3yiaJEfMHP9ysanA2rNW0SUkNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Being-VL-0.5 是一个多模态大模型（MLLM），通过一种称为视觉字节对编码（vBPE）的新方法，将文本和图像理解结合在一起。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与将图像和文本视为完全独立的模态不同，该方法直接对视觉标记应用 BPE 分词，从而创建更统一的表示，帮助模型更好地理解视觉和语言之间的关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/being-vl-0-5-3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/being-vl-0-5-3</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FireRedChat</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"474\" data-imgfileid=\"100016026\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.4101851851851852\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93f9e43e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOIPKtIfHfo47s1kymzsNiaQMdqV5UxicccyicunCqnrFWUb38kicU45S72Ew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FireRedChat 提供了一个完全自托管的解决方案，用于构建实时语音AI agnet。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它集成了强大的文本转语音（TTS）、自动语音识别（ASR）、个性化语音活动检测（pVAD）和端到端（EoT）功能，使开发者能够创建可定制的、注重隐私的AI agnet。该系统不依赖外部API，确保数据不泄漏，并提供完全的部署控制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fireredchat\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fireredchat</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：DeepScientist</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"466\" data-imgfileid=\"100016027\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.40370370370370373\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2943689&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOINOzib627I1cZJiaibmbwwBrXPuyndQYib8cevoxPXU8LyuiazgRFWDWBUoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepScientist 是一个旨在推动科学前沿的人工智能系统，其展示了 AI 在无需人类干预的情况下，通过目标导向的持续迭代科学发现，能够在多个领域超越人类的现有技术水平。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在 AI 文本检测领域，DeepScientist 在两周内取得了相当于人类三年研究的进展，并在 RAID 数据集上提高了 AUROC 分数，同时减少了推理延迟。此外，在“Agent Failure Attribution”任务中，DeepScientist 提出了名为 A2P 的新方法，实现了显著的性能提升。该项目的开源计划分为多个阶段，旨在为用户提供构建专业代理的基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepscientist\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepscientist</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：LIRA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"376\" data-imgfileid=\"100016030\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-ratio=\"0.32685185185185184\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=698dcbce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVibYd7rKpiadT5ksrNCvrOIOHy1k3WbX02ibJ4vpDQZiazbZUfHrMsjWZjqEMLB4XqLyHzvxEH95jLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LIRA是一种框架，旨在通过视觉理解和分割之间的互补关系来改善大规模多模态模型的分割和理解能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架通过语义增强特征提取器（SEFE）和交错局部视觉耦合（ILVC）两个关键组件来提高对象属性推断的准确性，并提供细粒度的监督以减少幻觉现象。此外，LIRA引入了属性评估（AttrEval）数据集，以量化对象分割精度与潜在相关语义之间的关系。实验表明，LIRA在分割和理解任务中达到了最先进的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lira\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lira</a></span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "汇总蚂蚁 Ling 2.0 系列万亿参数模型 Ling-1T、HunyuanVision 等开源 AI 基座、框架及 Agent 工具，聚焦高效推理与多模态理解。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "汇总蚂蚁 Ling 2.0 系列万亿参数模型 Ling-1T、HunyuanVision 等开源 AI 基座、框架及 Agent 工具，聚焦高效推理与多模态理解。",
  "summary": "文章以“今日开源”形式，集中介绍了多项 AI 前沿开源项目。蚂蚁 Ling 2.0 系列旗舰模型 Ling-1T 拥有万亿参数，支持 128K 长上下文，并采用进化链式思维（Evo-CoT）显著提升推理效率和深度。HunyuanVision-1.5 视觉语言模型，基于 mamba-transformer 混合架构，在多语言多模态理解和 3D 空间理解上表现卓越。Being-VL-0.5 通过视觉字节对编码（vBPE）实现视觉与语言的统一表示。在 AI Agent 领域，FireRedChat 提供自托管实时语音 AI Agent 解决方案，强调隐私保护；DeepScientist 则是一个通过自主迭代推动科学发现的 AI 系统。LIRA 框架通过创新组件，提升大规模多模态模型的分割与理解能力。本文为读者提供了一系列最新 AI 技术和工具的概览。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "蚂蚁开源万亿参数 Ling-1T，进化链式思维推动高效推理与长上下文。",
      "explanation": "Ling-1T 作为 Ling 2.0 系列旗舰，结合 Evo-CoT 过程和 128K 上下文，实现复杂推理 SOTA 性能，平衡了准确性与效率。"
    },
